92    /**
93     * Save document by name.
94     *
95     * @param string $filename
96     */
97    public function save($filename = null): void
98    {
99        $filename = $this->getTempFile($filename);
100        $zip = $this->getZipArchive($filename);
101        $phpWord = $this->getPhpWord();
102
103        // Content types
104        $this->contentTypes['default'] = [
105            'rels' => 'application/vnd.openxmlformats-package.relationships+xml',
106            'xml' => 'application/xml',
107        ];
108
109        // Add section media files
110        $sectionMedia = Media::getElements('section');
111        if (!empty($sectionMedia)) {
112            $this->addFilesToPackage($zip, $sectionMedia);
113            $this->registerContentTypes($sectionMedia);
114            foreach ($sectionMedia as $element) {
115                $this->relationships[] = $element;
116            }
117        }
118
119        // Add header/footer media files & relations
120        $this->addHeaderFooterMedia($zip, 'header');
121        $this->addHeaderFooterMedia($zip, 'footer');
122
123        // Add header/footer contents
124        $rId = Media::countElements('section') + 6; //@see Rels::writeDocRels for 6 first elements
125        $sections = $phpWord->getSections();
126        foreach ($sections as $section) {
127            $this->addHeaderFooterContent($section, $zip, 'header', $rId);
128            $this->addHeaderFooterContent($section, $zip, 'footer', $rId);
129        }
130
131        $this->addNotes($zip, $rId, 'footnote');
132        $this->addNotes($zip, $rId, 'endnote');
133        $this->addComments($zip, $rId);
134        $this->addChart($zip, $rId);
135
136        // Write parts
137        foreach ($this->parts as $partName => $fileName) {
138            if ($fileName != '') {
139                $zip->addFromString($fileName, $this->getWriterPart($partName)->write());
140            }
141        }
142
143        // Close zip archive and cleanup temp file
144        $zip->close();
145        $this->cleanupTempFile();
146    }

192    /**
193     * Add header/footer content.
194     *
195     * @param string $elmType header|footer
196     * @param int &$rId
197     */
198    private function addHeaderFooterContent(Section &$section, ZipArchive $zip, $elmType, &$rId): void
199    {
200        $getFunction = $elmType == 'header' ? 'getHeaders' : 'getFooters';
201        $elmCount = ($section->getSectionId() - 1) * 3;
202        $elements = $section->$getFunction();
203        /** @var \PhpOffice\PhpWord\Element\AbstractElement $element Type hint */
204        foreach ($elements as &$element) {
205            ++$elmCount;
206            $element->setRelationId(++$rId);
207            $elmFile = "{$elmType}{$elmCount}.xml"; // e.g. footer1.xml
208            $this->contentTypes['override']["/word/$elmFile"] = $elmType;
209            $this->relationships[] = ['target' => $elmFile, 'type' => $elmType, 'rID' => $rId];
210
211            /** @var \PhpOffice\PhpWord\Writer\Word2007\Part\AbstractPart $writerPart Type hint */
212            $writerPart = $this->getWriterPart($elmType)->setElement($element);
213            $zip->addFromString("word/$elmFile", $writerPart->write());
214        }
215    }

217    /**
218     * Add footnotes/endnotes.
219     *
220     * @param int &$rId
221     * @param string $noteType
222     */
223    private function addNotes(ZipArchive $zip, &$rId, $noteType = 'footnote'): void
224    {
225        $phpWord = $this->getPhpWord();
226        $noteType = ($noteType == 'endnote') ? 'endnote' : 'footnote';
227        $partName = "{$noteType}s";
228        $method = 'get' . $partName;
229        $collection = $phpWord->$method();
230
231        // Add footnotes media files, relations, and contents
232        /** @var \PhpOffice\PhpWord\Collection\AbstractCollection $collection Type hint */
233        if ($collection->countItems() > 0) {
234            $media = Media::getElements($noteType);
235            $this->addFilesToPackage($zip, $media);
236            $this->registerContentTypes($media);
237            $this->contentTypes['override']["/word/{$partName}.xml"] = $partName;
238            $this->relationships[] = ['target' => "{$partName}.xml", 'type' => $partName, 'rID' => ++$rId];
239
240            // Write relationships file, e.g. word/_rels/footnotes.xml
241            if (!empty($media)) {
242                /** @var \PhpOffice\PhpWord\Writer\Word2007\Part\AbstractPart $writerPart Type hint */
243                $writerPart = $this->getWriterPart('relspart')->setMedia($media);
244                $zip->addFromString("word/_rels/{$partName}.xml.rels", $writerPart->write());
245            }
246
247            // Write content file, e.g. word/footnotes.xml
248            $writerPart = $this->getWriterPart($partName)->setElements($collection->getItems());
249            $zip->addFromString("word/{$partName}.xml", $writerPart->write());
250        }
251    }

276     * Add chart.
277     *
278     * @param int &$rId
279     */
280    private function addChart(ZipArchive $zip, &$rId): void
281    {
282        $phpWord = $this->getPhpWord();
283
284        $collection = $phpWord->getCharts();
285        $index = 0;
286        if ($collection->countItems() > 0) {
287            /** @var \PhpOffice\PhpWord\Element\Chart $chart */
288            foreach ($collection->getItems() as $chart) {

291                $filename = "charts/chart{$index}.xml";
292
293                // ContentTypes.xml
294                $this->contentTypes['override']["/word/{$filename}"] = 'chart';
295
296                // word/_rels/document.xml.rel
297                $this->relationships[] = ['target' => $filename, 'type' => 'chart', 'rID' => $rId];
298
299                // word/charts/chartN.xml
300                $chart->setRelationId($rId);
301                $writerPart = $this->getWriterPart('Chart');
302                $writerPart->setElement($chart);
303                $zip->addFromString("word/{$filename}", $writerPart->write());
304            }

308    /**
309     * Register content types for each media.
310     *
311     * @param array $media
312     */
313    private function registerContentTypes($media): void
314    {
315        foreach ($media as $medium) {
316            $mediumType = $medium['type'];
317            if ($mediumType == 'image') {
318                $extension = $medium['imageExtension'];
319                if (!isset($this->contentTypes['default'][$extension])) {
320                    $this->contentTypes['default'][$extension] = $medium['imageType'];
321                }
322            } elseif ($mediumType == 'object') {
323                if (!isset($this->contentTypes['default']['bin'])) {
324                    $this->contentTypes['default']['bin'] = 'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.oleObject';
325                }
326            }
327        }
